      • emboss

        public static Bitmap emboss(Bitmap src,
            float lightDirection,
            float lightElevation,
            float bumpHeight,
            boolean emboss,
            Bitmap.Config outputConfig)
        Emboss the given bitmap
        Parameters:
        src -
        lightDirection - Direction of the light. min:0 max:360
        lightElevation - brightness. min:0 max:90
        bumpHeight - Height of the emobssed parts of the image. min:0 max:100
        emboss - if true, the bitmap is embossed retaining its color. else a grayscale image is embossed.
        outputConfig -
        Returns:
